      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/one-in-five-labour-voters-mull-switch-to-reform-uk-poll-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据一项新的调查，奈杰尔·法拉奇（Nigel Farage）的改革英国自去年大选以来就赢得了工党的选民赢得了胜利。]]></description>
