    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯说普京在美国敦促乌克兰休战时与特朗普交谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/kremlin-says-putin-to-speak-to-trump-as-us-pushes-ukraine-truce</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫证实，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）将于周二与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对话，这是在美国促使乌克兰战争停火的情况下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/kremlin-says-putin-to-speak-to-trump-as-us-pushes-ukraine-truce</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 11:15:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经合组织警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-s-trade-wars-tip-world-to-slower-growth-faster-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织说，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的积极贸易政策突然使世界迈向了增长速度较慢和通货膨胀率更高的道路，如果紧张局势升级，这可能会使世界越来越恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-s-trade-wars-tip-world-to-slower-growth-faster-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/romanian-far-right-would-lose-presidential-runoff-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项民意调查显示，罗马尼亚的中间派人士可以在5月的总统大选中激发对最右翼的支持，因为决定禁止唐纳德·特朗普政府盟友拥抱的超民族主义者震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/romanian-far-right-would-lose-presidential-runoff-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 08:51:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普驱逐了数百名敌人的法院谴责法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/trump-deports-hundreds-under-enemies-act-as-court-rebukes-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府周一坚持认为，委内瑞拉的特伦·德·阿拉古亚帮派的数百名成员被驱逐到萨尔瓦多被监禁，即使联邦法官下令停止某些驱逐出境，因此没有违反法院命令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/trump-deports-hundreds-under-enemies-act-as-court-rebukes-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:19:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
